---
title: Cheesy Pork Meatballs with Carrot Fries, Cucumber Slaw & Smokey Aioli
description: We got inspired by our American friends and their use of smokey, sweet and spiced flavours in Southwestern meals. That’s why
these meatballs are flavoured with our All-American spice blend, then served with crunchy slaw and carrot fries for a new,
low-carb take on dinner that will quickly become an instant classic.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
